<!-- Definition and uses -->
'''番瀉苷'''（{{lang|en|Senna glycosides}}，亦作{{lang|en|Sennosides}}或{{lang|en|Senna}}）也被稱為'''番瀉葉苷'''，為治療[[便秘|便秘]]的藥物，可用於手術前淨空[[大腸|大腸]]的藥物<ref name=AHFS2015>{{cite web|author1=American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|title=Senna|url=http://www.drugs.com/monograph/senna.html|website=Drugs.com|accessdate=11 August 2015|date=January 1, 2008|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906045617/http://www.drugs.com/monograph/senna.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，可經由口服或直腸給藥<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Ham2010/>。直腸給藥通常可於數分鐘內作用，口服則須約12小時<ref name=Nav2010/>。本品為較{{tsl|en|bisacodyl||比沙可啶}}或[[蓖麻油|蓖麻油]]溫和的瀉藥<ref name=AHFS2015/>。市面常見於油切茶、減肥茶或是便秘藥。

<!-- Adverse effects and mechanism -->
常見副作用包含腹部痙攣<ref name=Nav2010/>、上消化道出血、猛爆性肝炎，及產生依賴性。本品不建議長期使用，以避免引起腸功能受損或[[Electrolyte_problems|電解質流失]]<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。哺乳期間用藥目前仍無發現危害，但仍不建議使用<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。兒童不建議使用<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。使用本品會導致尿液偏紅<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。番瀉苷衍生物屬於[[泻药|刺激性緩瀉劑]]，為一種[[蒽醌|蒽醌]]<!-- <ref name=AHFS2015/> -->。目前該藥的作用機轉尚不清楚，普遍認為其藉由促進體液分泌及大腸收縮來達到其藥效<ref name=AHFS2015/>。

<!-- Society and culture -->
本品列名於[[世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单|世界卫生组织基本药物标准清单]]，為基礎公衛體系必備藥物之一<ref>{{cite web|title=19th WHO Model List of Essential Medicines|url=http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML2015_8-May-15.pdf|work=World Health Organization|accessdate=17 December 2015|date=April 2015|archive-date=2015-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150513043105/http://www.who.int/medicines/publications/essentialmedicines/EML2015_8-May-15.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。番瀉苷為價格低廉[[通用名药物|學名藥]]<ref name=AHFS2015/><ref name=Ham2010>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richard J.|title=Tarascon pharmacopoeia|date=2010|publisher=Jones and Bartlett|location=Sudbury, Mass.|isbn=9780763777685|page=181|edition=2010|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=Urmh7ylCXnoC&pg=PA181|access-date=2016-06-17|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305014932/https://books.google.ca/books?id=Urmh7ylCXnoC&pg=PA181|dead-url=no}}</ref>，每劑批發價約 0.01 美金<ref>{{cite web|title=Senna|url=http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=SEN7T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=7%2E5%20mg&desc=Senna&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=17%2E4%2E&supplement=&class_name=%2802%2E3%2E%29Medicines%20for%20other%20common%20symptoms%20in%20palliative%20care%3Cbr%3E%2817%2E4%2E%29Laxatives%3Cbr%3E|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=11 August 2015|archive-date=2020-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310080522/http://erc.msh.org/dmpguide/resultsdetail.cfm?language=english&code=SEN7T&s_year=2014&year=2014&str=7.5%20mg&desc=Senna&pack=new&frm=TAB-CAP&rte=PO&class_code2=17.4.&supplement=&class_name=%2802.3.%29Medicines%20for%20other%20common%20symptoms%20in%20palliative%20care%3Cbr%3E%2817.4.%29Laxatives|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。本品最早於[[決明屬|決明屬]]植物體內發現<ref name=Nav2010>{{cite book|last1=Navti|first1=Phyllis|title=Pharmacology for pharmacy and the health sciences : a patient-centred approach|date=2010|publisher=Oxford University Press|location=Oxford|isbn=9780199559824|page=337|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=KVicAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA337|access-date=2016-06-17|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023955/https://books.google.ca/books?id=KVicAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA337|dead-url=no}}</ref>，早在公元700年就有人使用<ref>{{cite book|last1=Khare|first1=C.P.|title=Indian Herbal Remedies Rational Western Therapy, Ayurvedic and Other Traditional Usage, Botany|date=2004|publisher=Springer Berlin Heidelberg|location=Berlin, Heidelberg|isbn=9783642186592|page=133|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=njLtCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA133|access-date=2016-06-17|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305030839/https://books.google.ca/books?id=njLtCAAAQBAJ&pg=PA133|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==概述==
番瀉苷是多種[[蒽醌|蒽醌]]類化合物衍生物的合稱，具輕瀉作用，是一種常見於植物內的天然[[瀉藥|瀉藥]]。番瀉苷是一種[[糖苷|糖苷]][[二聚體|二聚體]]，在[[決明屬|決明屬]]植物內的含量很豐富。決明屬植物如[[決明|決明]]、[[旃那|旃那]]等，其果子、豆筴、葉片等均可入藥，或作為瘦身茶飲的成份。
依台灣衛生署公告，番瀉苷於食品中，其每日食用限量為12毫克以下，孕婦、體虛者避免飲用<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ecosopp.com/product/zh_CN/4404/main.html |title=Oriyen 健美茶：介紹 |accessdate=2011-09-10 |language=zh-hans |publisher=[[eCosway|eCosway]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824035040/http://www.ecosopp.com/product/zh_CN/4404/main.html |archivedate=2011-08-24 }}</ref>。因此，當食品生產商要在台灣發售含有番瀉苷的食物或加工食物，需要為其食物檢測其番瀉苷含量，並於食物包裝上標明。


